場就在人民眼皮底下，讓視覺尬政權，奔放彩虹圖案對上冷硬政治口號，用想像力解放鐵幕之下停止跳動的心。"},{"pid":"560e9f8bc9a356eae3d6d5f0fe19c611b8650096","tid":1934062,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822d1c7ea5df14d6fc225e1eef5ddcf4f4f6f08f","tid":1934062,"uid":172465,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"你有冇見過盟軍海報<br />\n有希特拉個大頭之後大大個NO字原來係叫你去當兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞搞佢好喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T17:35:43.000Z","msg":"全民皆兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9bc71926e26121edbe9431b328ecc57b8c647f2","tid":1934062,"uid":13176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T17:45:44.000Z","msg":"離遠既話睇唔清柒婆個底，睇落似叫人唔好登記做選民咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好咩？"},{"pid":"be389189484e372524356e5ff903cfbe011c803e","tid":1934062,"uid":260377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T17:53:17.000Z","msg":"係咪因為之前幾張都比人hi屎上去"},{"pid":"db6bfc22e0177eee0678bbaea70798c58c9dd7f2","tid":1934062,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T17:55:41.000Z","msg":"幾靚,個色幾出"},{"pid":"0c2ea450b403cdcae2f32228c3e73ba0af39c7a8","tid":1934062,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be389189484e372524356e5ff903cfbe011c803e","tid":1934062,"uid":260377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T17:53:17.000Z","msg":"係咪因為之前幾張都比人hi屎上去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:31:53.000Z","msg":"歡迎藍絲hi屎落林鄭個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408fd7bb5a0b1c6c6035e7fd73e1694f26ba72a8","tid":1934062,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d94ffe6592a3647d06e7434b8288e0467b3e89bc","tid":1934062,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"想睇牙晴對害羞的波"},{"pid":"3162